{"tid":2499432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"乍德總統戰死 反抗軍將進攻首都籲回歸民主","createTime":"2021-04-22T01:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"63588123657ccc6b0bae3ea46c8837072cb915b8","tid":2499432,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:22:02.000Z","msg":"查德掌權30年的總統德比（Idriss Deby）與反抗分子作戰時在20日傷重不治，他的兒子馬哈哈邁特&middot;卡卡（Mahamat Kaka）在今（21）日接任總統，反抗軍則表示，他們將前進首都恩將納（N'Djamena），讓國家回歸民主。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，查德軍方在德比身亡後宣布實施宵禁、關閉邊境，以及全國哀悼14天。儘管在首都恩將納上的商店與學校，今天都維持正常運作，未停止上班上課，但是許多人都待在屋內。<br />\n<br />\n總部位在利比亞的「查德變革與協和陣線」（FACT）表示，他們仍在卡奈姆大區（Kanem），但正準備進攻恩將納，並拒絕當局政府所提出的軍事過渡計畫（ military's transition plan），從不民主的體系中「解放」查德。<br />\n<br />\nFACT強調，「查德不是君主制」、他們並不想要奪權掌政，「我們的目標是使民主過渡成為現實」。發言人說，「我們拿起武器是因為查德沒有民主空間，且難以想像有和平解決方案。」<br />\n<br />\n人權觀察 （Human Rights Watch）認為，「國際過去曾支持查德政府的反恐行動，但卻對高壓統治與石油管控問題，甚至鎮壓反對人士，都視而不見」，德比曾於2018年推動通過新憲法，得以讓他掌權至2033年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3507163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3507163&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=afb8c093\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3507163&h=30c6ac98\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3507163</a>"},{"pid":"0d81685a474f12feba97c6f691d79942a0030a23","tid":2499432,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"非洲國家？"},{"pid":"5c1a4afac4447396aa27471288a69cd150744677","tid":2499432,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d81685a474f12feba97c6f691d79942a0030a23","tid":2499432,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"非洲國家？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"71ea4843986af87672f60668d45f4e30a7871fc3","tid":2499432,"uid":32722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"世界越來越亂, 越來越多國家玩內戰<br />\n好快到我地好熟識既國家"},{"pid":"5c1d654838a76fc76132624d9732e5cbe19741b4","tid":2499432,"uid":3581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71ea4843986af87672f60668d45f4e30a7871fc3","tid":2499432,"uid":32722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"世界越來越亂, 越來越多國家玩內戰<br />\n好快到我地好熟識既國家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"個啲地方一路都無平靜過"},{"pid":"e56a033eb7502eff4fd2bfe85df74724fe502f5d","tid":2499432,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"總司令上前線比人伏？"},{"pid":"268a6e92eb8a992705bb63a3a6045e6792981f7d","tid":2499432,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"乍得總統係國民黨軍閥既話，呢班反抗軍就比較似講民主既共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81025428558c2388b693a7a194470a307c068dc7","tid":2499432,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd9nH7JBT5DNb1nUcmFdhLSvxnTdRcr5eTSmSGpiLZ3MJ?filename=EwYGUmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwYGUmT.jpg&h=2affedaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc3c4dc925766c9041ebae459b7a6b2bfffbfbaf","tid":2499432,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1d654838a76fc76132624d9732e5cbe19741b4","tid":2499432,"uid":3581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71ea4843986af87672f60668d45f4e30a7871fc3","tid":2499432,"uid":32722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"世界越來越亂, 越來越多國家玩內戰<br />\n好快到我地好熟識既國家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"個啲地方一路都無平靜過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"2005年停過火，但之後都打返，有利比亞同親俄勢力作亂，乍得算係法國地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.g